title: Using Powershell.org provided instance of TeamCity
---

PowerShell.org offers an instance of TeamCity, free to use for any PowerShell project with an approved open-source license. 
This is similar to other hosted Continuous Integration services out there, such as Appveyor and teamcity.codebetter.com, 
but with some advantages for the PowerShell community:

